{"tid":747680,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU與KakaoM完成續約...傳聞是8:2分賬 藝人是8","createTime":"2018-07-18T14:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T16:03:46.000Z","uid":34643,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"23d6ba86478ed8abd326d9fb41a219ce7004bbf1","tid":747680,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:31:32.000Z","msg":"18日，KakaoM方面表示：&ldquo;IU在最近與我社完成了續約工作，今後將作為KakaoM的專屬藝人一起前行&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，在IU與所屬社深厚的互相信賴情況下，在合約到期前幾個月就進行了續約工作。據悉，續約是很迅速做下的決定。這也是IU從出道時期開始就與所屬社KakaoM（舊：Loen）一起，延續了10年的義氣。<br />\n<br />\nKakaoM方面表示：&ldquo;與IU長時間一直維持伙伴關系真的非常高興。今後也會為IU作為優秀的藝人與演員，開展更加有意義的活動而不遺余力地提供支持&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.topstarnews.net/news/photo/201803/377712_22163_4247_org.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.topstarnews.net%2Fnews%2Fphoto%2F201803%2F377712_22163_4247_org.jpg&h=53211458&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cfecc297eb724aec42c19d1abf2652fd1e8e73b","tid":747680,"uid":72076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:34:15.000Z","msg":"霸氣外露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68778759ecc4a2c569b7884517fdeab376a9627","tid":747680,"uid":8612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"公司2咁少！"},{"pid":"c47571763a4a9a126806bac965db2b823aa9617c","tid":747680,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b550d621046d492d4f0a8babf274451d2799dd1d","tid":747680,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e68778759ecc4a2c569b7884517fdeab376a9627","tid":747680,"uid":8612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"公司2咁少！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:54:50.000Z","msg":"差唔多, 咁多種藝人係團體係分得特別少, 歌手演員同公司55對分左右, 但kakao整鳩我iu一獲, 賠一世都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_conne